This publication is the official booklet for the "Wings Over Arkansas" award program.
A free service to the residents of Arkansas.
Fullcolor certificates are awarded to birdwatchers who report their life list of Arkansas birds to the Arkansas Game 
If you are interested in learning more about this program, please call (870) 424-5750 or e-mail pspeer@agfc.state.ar.us An application may be obtained by calling (501) 223-6351 or downloaded from the Arkansas Game and Fish Web Page at: www.agfc.com.
