A very special thanks to the Arkansas Audubon Society for allowing me to incorporate their Field List in this brochure.
Also to Douglas A. James and Joseph C. Neal for writing ARKANSAS BIRDS Â­ Their Distribution and Abundance, an excellent reference book and to Mel White for his outstanding publication, A Birder's Guide to Arkansas.
Also, the American Birding Association for providing ethical guidelines to make it a better birding world for us all.
All were very helpful in compiling this checklist.
Please, take the time to share the world of birding with a child.
Everyone will reap the rewards for generations to come.
Happy Birding, Phyllis Speer Outreach Programs Coordinator Arkansas Game 
